{"tid":368751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"窮撚生存方式 勁過3餐m記","createTime":"2017-08-21T18:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T00:15:40.000Z","uid":137997,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb52ac67eaca503a41fb96d4eb1ee28b36b5a837","tid":368751,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:51:40.000Z","msg":"每日只用廿蚊<br />\n忽略水電煤價錢健康味道問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五包裝營多 十一蚊<br />\n果然系系列飲品六包裝 九個九（夠飲兩日）<br />\n仲有幾蚊突出來買下水果或者儲起佢<br />\n香蕉一條都仲夠錢買<br />\n<br />\n早餐食一包營多+飲品一包<br />\n午餐兩包+飲品一包<br />\n晚餐兩包+飲品一包 <br />\n<br />\n只要用以上方法食十年死唔去 應該上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8698ce1f817f65a9c85f1a622acc3adf0b2e316c","tid":368751,"uid":72638,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:52:55.000Z","msg":"賢者之石"},{"pid":"a11227bb4d3071b09d28ddf12b53fdc4bfe53154","tid":368751,"uid":65587,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:53:41.000Z","msg":"黑箱車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a9d2e55377cb1b0491f5a102a76aedb2ace90a","tid":368751,"uid":137997,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T18:56:53.000Z","msg":"好耐之前真係試過 屋企人返哂大陸 掉抵一百蚊係到就算 我又唔知佢地幾時返 得張字條同錢 頂左唔知幾多日先獲救 差啲死係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57af8b7605b628407e51c46b9dcba4c1be8c1e6","tid":368751,"uid":96303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:02:16.000Z","msg":"福麵好似平啲同大份啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ce98a4d3fbc47b8283b0fd5b6c52d207f3a814","tid":368751,"uid":28624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T19:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔駛幾年就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa91d11bb8af3ab4a208bf5eb6517d8ba813c30c","tid":368751,"uid":137997,"like":1,"disl